&lt;li&gt;Drive strategic SKU addition decisions based on application coverage, demand signals, and margin contribution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead SKU rationalization reviews to maintain a healthy, focused product portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
