&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Marketing, Communications, Multimedia, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3–5 years of experience in social media content creation, videography, photography, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in visual storytelling and branding for consumer products, preferably in the automotive or lifestyle industries.&lt;/li&gt;
